OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784063895
OL,3,CWhat security do MPs have?
OL,5,FCounter terrorism police confirmed on
OL,6,FTuesday she was killed in a "targeted
OL,7,Fattack", adding that whether the
OL,8,Fsuspect was targeting Reform UK
OL,9,Ffigures will be a "line of inquiry".
OL,11,FA 28-year-old white British man
OL,12,Fremains under arrest on suspicion of
OL,13,Fcommission, preparation, or
OL,14,Finstigation of acts of terrorism, as
OL,15,Fwell as on suspicion of murder, Head
OL,16,Fof Counter Terrorism Policing,
OL,17,FAssistant Commissioner Laurence Taylor
OL,18,Fsaid.
OL,26,@qD@SOUqD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/22
