OL,3,CWhat security do MPs have?
OL,5,FReform UK has since announced it is
OL,6,Fproviding all of its MPs with round-
OL,7,Fthe-clock security amid fears for
OL,8,Ftheir safety.
OL,10,FJune marked ten years since the murder
OL,11,Fof Labour MP Jo Cox, and her sister,
OL,12,FMP Kim Leadbeater, urged politicians
OL,13,Fto "push back on the divisive rhetoric
OL,14,Fand the dangerous language" that has
OL,15,Frisen since her sister's killing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
