CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784063895
OL,3,CWhat security do MPs have?
OL,5,FA spokesperson for the prime minister
OL,6,Fsaid it is clear that no politician
OL,7,Fshould be targeted or face abuse,
OL,8,Fregardless of their views and that
OL,9,Fpoliticians should be able to do their
OL,10,Fvital work safely and free of
OL,11,Fintimidation.
OL,13,FWhat threats do MPs face?
OL,15,FThe murders of two MPs in their
OL,16,Fconstituency - Labour's Jo Cox in 2016
OL,17,Fand Conservative MP David Amess in
OL,18,F2021 - have led to a significant
OL,19,Fexpansion of security measures for MPs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784063895
OL,3,CWhat security do MPs have?
OL,5,FThere have been multiple instances of
OL,6,Fpeople prosecuted and even jailed for
OL,7,Fmaking threats to MPs across the
OL,8,Fpolitical spectrum in recent years,
OL,9,Faccording to the Institute for
OL,10,FGovernment (IfG).
OL,12,FThese threats include death and rape
OL,13,Fthreats sent to MPs via social media
OL,14,Fand email, and there have even been
OL,15,Fplots to carry out murders.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784063895
OL,3,CWhat security do MPs have?
OL,5,FA report from the 2025 Speaker's
OL,6,FConference on the Security of
OL,7,FCandidates, MPs and Elections found
OL,8,Fthat 96% of the 224 surveyed MPs had
OL,9,Freceived some form of abuse since
OL,10,Fbeing elected, most commonly abusive
OL,11,Flanguage and insults.
OL,13,FIt also revealed that 27% of MPs said
OL,14,Fthey had received death threats and
OL,15,F37% reported threats to harm them.
OL,17,FSpeaking in the Commons on Monday,
OL,18,Fveteran MP Dianne Abbott said that at
OL,19,Fone point she "got as many threats and
OL,20,Fabuse and threats of violence as all
OL,21,Fthe other women MPs put together".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784063895
OL,3,CWhat security do MPs have?
OL,5,FCrediting her experience in her nearly
OL,6,F40 years as an MP and the first black
OL,7,Fwoman to be elected to the Commons,
OL,8,FAbbott said that the problem has got
OL,9,F"much, much worse" and said it is
OL,10,Flikely related to the rise in online
OL,11,Fabuse.
OL,13,FData collected by the Speaker's
OL,14,FConference found that female MPs and
OL,15,Fthose from minority backgrounds are
OL,16,Fmore likely to be targeted.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
