FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784063895
OL,3,CWhat security do MPs have?
OL,5,FOut of the Black, Asian and minority
OL,6,Fethnic MPs, 56% reported feeling
OL,7,Funsafe during the 2024 election
OL,8,Fperiod, higher than the overall
OL,9,Fproportions of new and returning MPs,
OL,10,Fwhere only 25% and 42% felt unsafe,
OL,11,Frespectively.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, 26% of women reported
OL,14,Fexperiences of sexual harassment, and
OL,15,F14% of women experienced threats of
OL,16,Fsexual violence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
